  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网设备预约系统设计一个状态流转图。核心是从ActuatorController开始，用户创建预约草稿，然后提交进入待审核状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Draft",
        "Pending"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是ActuatorController，用户触发创建后进入Draft。Pending状态之后需要管理员介入吗？还是系统自动处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Draft",
        "Pending",
        "Admin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Pending需要管理员或系统审批，通过就到Confirmed，拒绝则到Rejected。另外Rejected之后要回到ActuatorController，表示流程结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Confirmed",
        "Rejected",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Pending的分支我画好了。Confirmed之后呢？用户实际使用设备时应该有个进行中的状态吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Confirmed",
        "InProgress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Confirmed之后有两种情况：到达开始时间且用户签到，进入InProgress；或者用户提前取消，到Cancelled。还有一种特殊情况——超时未签到，标记为NoShow。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Confirmed",
        "InProgress",
        "Cancelled",
        "NoShow",
        "check-in"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Confirmed的三个出口我确认了：InProgress、Cancelled、NoShow。InProgress之后呢？正常结束和异常取消都要考虑吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "Completed",
        "Cancelled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，InProgress正常结束到Completed，然后回到ActuatorController。紧急情况可以取消到Cancelled，但Cancelled要走PLC_Logic处理，不是直接回控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "Completed",
        "Cancelled",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "注意到NoShow和Rejected也是回到ActuatorController，只有Cancelled特殊处理。另外需要加注释说明Pending时的邮件通知和InProgress时的资源锁定吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "InProgress",
        "email notification",
        "resources locked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Pending状态要触发邮件通知给用户和管理员，InProgress时资源要锁定给当前用户。这两个注释加在对应状态右侧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "InProgress",
        "email",
        "resources"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部完成了。从ActuatorController出发，经过Draft、Pending的分支审批，Confirmed后的三种流向，最终通过Completed、NoShow、Rejected回到控制器，Cancelled走PLC_Logic，两个关键状态的注释也加上了。",
